{"type":"message","id":"d2b35bae","parentId":"d94a5733","timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:49:38.417Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1vf18vroe7d1_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5410\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3308\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] temporal_invariant_classifier.py\r\n[mutation proposed] temporal_invariant_classifier.py\r\n[master 2f75209] pulse: 2026-03-23 224905\n 7 files changed, 353 insertions(+), 85 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-23 224905.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-23 224905.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-23 223905.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-23 224905 - The COMPRESSION-CAUSAL DUALITY insight suggests that invariant detection IS causal discovery. The next critical step is implementing a TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) classifier that can identify what persists across pulse gaps versus what decays.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"quick-bison","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5410\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3308\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] temporal_invariant_classifier.py\r\n[mutation proposed] temporal_invariant_classifier.py\r\n[master 2f75209] pulse: 2026-03-23 224905\n 7 files changed, 353 insertions(+), 85 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-23 224905.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-23 224905.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-23 223905.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-23 224905 - The COMPRESSION-CAUSAL DUALITY insight suggests that invariant detection IS causal discovery. The next critical step is implementing a TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) classifier that can identify what persists across pulse gaps versus what decays.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwma